
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <title>Event Manager Thanks You!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="text-align: center">
    <h1>Thanks <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>Thanks for coming to our conference.  We couldn't have done it without you!</p>

    <p>Political activism is at the heart of any democracy and your voice needs to be heard. Please consider reaching out to your nearby representatives.</p>
    <br>
    <p style="font-size: 21px">Local legislators at Zipcode: <%= zipcode %></p>
    <p><% legislators.each do |legislator| %></p>

    <p style="font-weight: bold"><%= "#{legislator.first_name} #{legislator.last_name}" %></p>
    <p><%= "#{legislator.website}" %></p>
    <p><% end %></p>
  </body>
</html>